snippet.title: Apes vs. Zombies ape king Kong Bazooka invasion Gameplay
snippet.description:
InApes vs. Zombies, you'l help our chief
ape "Kong" defend his kingdom against the
impending zombie invasion and resque your
girlfriend Jane. What are you waiting for?
Grab your bazooka and round up your monkey
friends to givethe zombies a goodrun for
their money and free your Jane.
